代该姓名人几乎都是政客，而且该姓者只有几百人。剧情里的下层日军为该姓，随便赐该姓给汉奸不妥吧？ 3近卫，古摄政贵族藤原氏的后人，五摄家之一，作为普通下层日军的姓说不过去了吧？现在民间该姓者多为笔名，艺名 4龟田，抗战剧里几乎无处不在，简直成了世界观里的日本大姓，可现实中不算常见，甚至龟井，龟冈，大龟之类龟字姓的人口都比它多。设想下日本人拍了一部剧表现20世纪的中国军人，结果世界观里夏侯，诸葛，司马，太史这些复姓是大姓，李王张刘这些反倒是小姓会怎样？ 5井道崎，现实中日本无此姓，属于杜撰（日本那么多姓还不够做素材的？还要瞎编？）"},"attached_info":"Cj8IhOqnzr/C+9UnEAMaCDY4MDQ3NjA0IJCqi4gGMAo42gFALnIJNDc1OTUyOTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"45 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-31c9d9d60eeca9109cc338c8f7b88087_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"47_1631516897.4900076","card_id":"Q_479248319","target":{"id":479248319,"title":"您有哪些非常喜欢的暖心的励志句子？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/479248319","type":"question","created":1628754629,"answer_count":85,"follower_count":182,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[668,15344,114127,285235],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IhOqnzr/C+9UnEAMaCDY4NzgwOTI1IMWl04gGMAA4tgFAL3IJNDc5MjQ4MzE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"45 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-61e4b281bdf49853e2256eab6347753b_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"48_1631516897.4904008","card_id":"Q_41865668","target":{"id":41865668,"title":"考研要准备多长时间?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/41865668","type":"question","created":1459134865,"answer_count":83,"follower_count":891,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[988],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我是师大地理科学专业的学生，现在大二，想要考研人文地理学，但大三下学期还有顶岗实习，那考研要什么时候开始准备呢"},"attached_info":"Cj0IhOqnzr/C+9UnEAMaBzg5NTM4NDYgkcPitwUwBDj7BkAwcgg0MTg2NTY2OHgAqgEJ